channel.title: Need help with Silabsofts client. :\
channel.description:
Ok, well I fixed my last problem with this client, and got it running.
At first, I got an error when I clicked run.bat
But now I can load the client up and play on it, but the new items show up. The people are just invisible, just like the MoparScape 3.2 client.
I got a picture here of what the run.bat says when I click on it, it's under the Cache Modifications.
Here is the image.
[URL=http://img341.imageshack.us/my.php?image=erroragainfn8.png][IMG]http://img341.imageshack.us/img341/2932/erroragainfn8.th.png[/img][/URL]
Also, from what the error says, I [b][u]THINK[/u][/b] it's failing to download the Silabsoft modifications. Also it says ' java.io.FileNotFoundException ' which I don't know what it means, unless it can't find a file... Or if not, there has to be a different solution. :\ And it says ' The System cannot find the path specified ' Which I don't know what that means. >.< Yeah I'm a nub lol.
It would be nice if someone were to help me. If you know the solution, post or PM me. :) If you would rather discuss it over MSN PM me and I'll tell you it.
Thank-you. :)
